descriptionHTML:
A watchface unlike any you've ever seen before. Travel outerspace with this fancypants watch. It's the successor of Planetary. Make sure you check out the motion sensor! Tilt your watch left/right/up/down. features: Top: Sunrise, Sunset Bottom: Lo Temp, Hi temp, Humidity.

Powered by Facer
Facer Watch Faces is the ultimate watch face customization platform for Android Wear & Tizen smartwatches. Facer offers everything you need to customize & personalize your Android Watch or Gear S2/S3, including 15,000 free and premium watch faces from leading brands and artists. You can even make your own watch faces and share them with the world using the creator tool. Don’t be default, Facer offers everything you’ll need to bring your personal style to your smartwatch.

FEEDBACK & TROUBLESHOOTING
  • *If you’re having any issues using our app & watch faces or are dissatisfied in any way, please give us a chance to fix it for you before expressing dissatisfaction through ratings.
  • *You can send feedback directly to facer-support@little-labs.com
  • *If you are enjoying our watch faces, we always appreciate a positive review

    COMPATIBLE WITH ALL ANDROID WEAR WATCHES
    Facer watch faces are compatible with all of the latest Android Wear devices, including Nixon Mission, Polar m600, Michael Kors Smartwatch, Asus Zenwatch 3, Moto 360 Sport, Casio WSD-F10, Tag Heuer Smartwatch, Moto 360 1 & Moto 360 2nd gen, Huawei Android watch, Asus Zen Watch 1 & 2, Sony Smartwatch 3, LG G Android watch, LG G R Android watch, LG Urbane smartwatch, Samsung Gear smartwatch and more
